      "children": [
        {
          "textSize": "heading-two",
          "text": "SpokenWeb Manifesto 2025"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "textSize": "heading-two",
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "At the end of the Sound Institute, the SpokenWeb team came together to record a manifesto. Loosely using the prompt "
        },
        {
          "text": "SpokenWeb is...",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": ", each attendee was invited to share a thought, a feeling, a micro-poem — any expression of their feelings about SpokenWeb and the past seven years of the partnership."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Watch the 2025 SpokenWeb Manifesto, recorded in 360°.",
          "link": "https://ndamours14.github.io/360resounding/events/spokenweb-manifesto-2025/"
        }
